{"type": "article", "id": 18495, "title": "铁花窗元素的餐具", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-04T07:40:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060037454tpuwfiVLIGSZlMY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是台湾的文创品牌布菈瑟 Blossom 推出的一套餐具，他们从铁花窗处获得灵感，在交接处往往要转折成一个平面。而这些叉、勺、刀的手柄也在握住的地方翻转 90 度变成另一个平面，靠着特殊的焊接工艺实现，有旧时的韵味。布菈瑟近期要在台中开一家小店，搜集各地的铁花窗的图片，这是为这组餐具增添一份故事。产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.zeczec.com/projects/blossom\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060037425WLz2AshYnT8Ho3U.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003743O0TiscoYCGAzjlyV.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003744gWpASKMoNuOJPRdm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}